  How To Order
  ~~~~~~~~~~~~

  You may place an order (or pre-order) by writing to;

  Arrow Pd
   P.O. Box 7
    Dover
     Kent
      CT15 4AP                         E-mail: ccg@arrowpd.demon.co.uk


  Postage and packing is 75p on any sized order within the UK
                          (1.50UKP for the rest of the world)
 


         Please make all cheques/POs/IMO payable to 'Arrow Pd'
 (Please note that if paying by cheque, allow seven days for clearance
 for all orders over 10UKP)


  Don't forget to add your name and address to any orders. Thank you.



  Goods are offered subject to availability and subject to price
  alteration without notice.                  
